title: DDFP 351: Top 5 QBs & bold AFC predictions
itunes:title: DDFP 351: Top 5 QBs & bold AFC predictions
description:
Shek is joined by former NFL scout and player Bucky Brooks to discuss how the NFL Draft impacts the AFC as they make bold playoff predictions (14:10). The guys also debate the top 5 quarterbacks in the league as Bucky says Tom Brady is no longer in the elite group (32:30).
